rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0001
rows.name: Gwin-san.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0002
rows.name:
Lin-chan, you're already here?
Even with such a huge horde you had to fight?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0003
rows.name: Guys like that are easy work, meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0004
rows.name: Guys like that are easy work, meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0005
rows.name: I'll make breakfast out of you[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0006
rows.name:
Colonel Elma,
Thank you for the backup.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0007
rows.name:
Likewise.
More importantly, where are Iriina and Marcus?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0008
rows.name: They're near the Life Point over there, but[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0009
rows.name: Are you guys the only ones here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0010
rows.name: Yeah, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0011
rows.name:
Strange.
I thought the main force was somewhere else.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0012
rows.name: Could it be[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0013
rows.name:
Iriina! Marcus!
Run!![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0014
rows.name: Huh!?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0015
rows.name: Marcus![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0016
rows.name: Right![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0041
rows.name:
Aww, too bad.
Do primitive species have sharp intuition, I wonder?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0042
rows.name: That voice... The woman from Nightglow Forest![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0043
rows.name: The main force was elsewhere... just as I suspected.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0044
rows.name: I see... Oh well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0045
rows.name:
I just need to crush you bastards
with this unit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0046
rows.name: You used the Life Point to lure us into a trap...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0047
rows.name: It's a little different from a trap.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0048
rows.name: My goal is... seeing that kind of faces.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0049
rows.name:
I want to see Earthlings' faces
twisted in despair like that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0050
rows.name: Earthlings are an eyesore, you see.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0051
rows.name:
Though what's truly an eyesore are
the flesh-and-blood Earthlings.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0053
rows.name:
Well, even destroying manufactured puppets like you
is fun, so I'll do it anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0054
rows.name: That's all![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0055
rows.name: You know about B.Bs. and the Life Point...?

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0056
rows.name:
I know.
Because there's someone quite well-informed working with me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0057
rows.name: That's why I also understand the reason Earthlings are panicking.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0058
rows.name: There's a limit to the operational time, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0059
rows.name: The operational limit of the so-called Life Point.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0060
rows.name:
If I wait for that, you bastards
will all become unable to move.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0061
rows.name: Truthfully, I could just wait for that, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0062
rows.name:
smashing that thing right in front of you Earthlings
is also fu[ST:wide ]―![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0063
rows.name: Be silent, Samaar barbarian![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0064
rows.name:
Your arrogance
has caused many tragedies throughout the universe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0065
rows.name: I won't let that tragedy happen again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0066
rows.name:
You're just an Earthling,
what could you possibly know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0067
rows.name: Defeat that one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0068
rows.name: Iriina's team, take the surrounding Dolls![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07060100_MSG0069
rows.name: Right![ST:wait ]
